textfsm_template:
Value Required LOCAL_PORT (\S+)
Value INT_NAME (.*?)
Value INT_TYPE (.*?)
Value TRUNK (\S+)
Value TRUNK_TYPE (\S+)

Start
  ^\s*Load\sBalancing\sMethod.*$$
  ^\s+Port\s+|\s+Name\s+Type\s+|\s+Group\s+Type.*$$
  ^\s+-+\s+\+\s+\-+.* -> TRUNKS
  ^\s*$$
  ^. -> Error

TRUNKS
  ^\s+${LOCAL_PORT}\s+\|\s${INT_NAME}\s+ ${INT_TYPE}\s+ \|\s${TRUNK}\s+${TRUNK_TYPE}.*$$ -> Record
  ^\S+\#\s*$$
  ^\s*$$
  ^. -> Error
